{"type": "article", "id": 32274, "title": "你见过有弹性的积木吗？｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2016-09-17T23:03:21Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 28678, "name": "Rosenthal"}, {"id": 32828, "name": "Achodoso"}, {"id": 32829, "name": "DANTE-Goods And Bads"}, {"id": 32830, "name": "Joan Rojeski"}, {"id": 32831, "name": "senscommon"}, {"id": 3208, "name": "Normann Copenhagen"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 4, "praise_count": 131, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160918101756u3aIrDcXlHR4TSnK.jpg", "contents": "<p class=\"\">          </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>In_Tube Wall Hook by Achodoso</h3><p>西班牙的 <a href=\"http://achodoso.es/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Achodoso</a> 工作室最近研发了一种名为 In_Tube 的工艺：在一段弯曲的金属圆管上切出一个口子，它的大小刚好足够一根和圆管直径相当的木管插入。丰富的色彩搭配以及制作工艺所特有的视觉效果使这套同名的<a href=\"http://achodoso.es/portfolio/in_tube-wall-hook/\" rel=\"nofollow\">壁钩</a>看上去就好像是一道道凝结的彩虹，使用起来非常灵活。这是它的<a href=\"https://www.crowdyhouse.com/shop/in_tube-wall-hook/\" rel=\"nofollow\">购买链接</a>，售价为 35 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201609172356361JorQRVzqDbm2PTS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667482\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160917235637pfmD5StQqOy6YeuR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.790954\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160917235637YJMS4pKWbtmyeCvw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160917235636uDk69eLZtlQ74UsP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667482\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160917235636zeN10Fak6mAnobSp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160917235636CRAuQvfzHB0p6S8k.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667482\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Nightingale by Rosenthal</h3><p>在巴黎家居博览会秋展上，德国品牌 <a href=\"https://www.rosenthal.de/en/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Rosenthal</a> 展出了这款与 <a href=\"http://www.dante.lu/\" rel=\"nofollow\">DANTE-Goods And Bads</a> 工作室联手打造的环形台灯 <a href=\"http://www.dante.lu/dante/portfolio/nightingale-3\" rel=\"nofollow\">Nightingale</a>。垂直翻转 90 度的陶瓷灯罩颠覆了常见的台灯造型，同时也改变了灯光的呈现形式。附在外圈的皮带既是装饰，又是提手，可以像提着一盏古董灯那样移动，相当优雅。这是它的<a href=\"https://www.rosenthal.de/en/shop/products-en/home-accessories/lamps-en/\" rel=\"nofollow\">购买链接</a>，售价根据大小（高 27 或 42 厘米）分别为 619 和 829 欧元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160917235601PWxBQOXlM1Zdzpaf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160917235559JeiEntL2MflWqT6S.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160917235559l6SdEHYoZKNsM47R.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160917235559N07hFakeGLMbcoI5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.777506\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160917235559CUAxD2R4LpPQf6jy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750611\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201609172356003C5vnHV1q9WPF6hi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.770171\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Sticky notes by Joan Rojeski</h3><p>如果你觉得市面上现有的便利贴还不够有趣的话，西班牙 <a href=\"http://www.joanrojeski.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Joan Rojeski</a> 工作室最近为丹麦品牌 <a href=\"http://www.normann-copenhagen.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Normann Copenhagen</a> 旗下的 Daily Collection 所设计的五款便利贴或许会通过它们极具创意的造型让你眼前一亮：只要沿着便利贴上不同色区的界线折叠，它们就可以从普通的贴纸变为传递秘密的信封、手提包、小册子、纸飞机或是一栋小屋。不仅实用，还能装点桌面。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160917235525DmyqjvWMaCEsrd17.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.629584\" data-format=\"gif\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160917235523VO9ERlBtoPmGwDeT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201609172355236SFtr2LQpvm1PXdW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667482\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160917235524Fz0JgilCU1L4OtfI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.705379\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160917235523XwglJG6R8p2AaLeF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667482\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160917235524UK4TzLyJcqYVSatj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667482\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Cyclist Raincoat by senscommon</h3><p>来自荷兰的 Laura Šilinska 不仅是一名狂热的自行车骑手，更是一位非常注重细节的服装设计师，她断断续续花费了四年时间设计了这款名为 Cyclist Raincoat 的雨衣，就曾入围 2014 年的无印良品设计奖。这款男女均可穿着的雨衣不仅外观时尚，功能上同样非常出色：它使用的是一种由设计团队 <a href=\"http://www.senscommon.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">senscommon</a> 和纺织品制造商 Koojoo 共同研发的材料，由 57% 的尼龙和 43% 的涤纶混合而成，既柔软又轻薄；为了避免骑行时雨衣随风飞扬，两侧下摆都配备了搭扣；左右手肘处还使用了反光性的黑色墨水，在夜间骑行时可以起到向后方示意的作用。你可以通过<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/senscommon/cyclist-raincoat-your-urban-lifestyle-essential\" rel=\"nofollow\">链接</a>参与众筹，早鸟价为 160 欧元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160917235258y5JYuaPMX94RHLnv.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"gif\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160917235258h7qNiaeGuIJC5Ky3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.547059\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160917235300o37qMnedPZ8FXsRc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160917235300PJT3dmGUN68EWKjI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562347\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160917235334ULPVT3oum4zqGfry.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562347\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>MR.ORANGE by Pasini &amp; Peckelsen</h3><p>你有没有幻想过把吸管插到橙子里就能喝到果汁？由两位德国工程师设计的工具套装 <a href=\"http://www.mrorange.eu/\" rel=\"nofollow\">MR.ORANGE</a> 可以让你轻松地完成这个梦想。套装包含了一根可机洗的铝合金吸管和一块用来固定的橡胶盖，将吸管穿过盖子捣碎果肉，就可以吸到新鲜的果汁了。MR.ORANGE 目前正处于专利申请阶段，你可以通过<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/mr-orange/mr-orange-a-new-drinking-experience\" rel=\"nofollow\">链接</a>参与众筹，早鸟价为 8 欧元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160917235214MjSz8i1KFrChZkmL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.563333\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160917235214SYedW2VoGzOCFJqs.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.300000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160917235215gxm5VWZfbijQ6ehM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.563235\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160917235215Nq5ZiYBwRMsTkfo3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.563235\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160917235215v6oAriZctMbQ41UJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.560294\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Flexo by Team Flexo</h3><p>来自新西兰的 Mark Stolten 一直抱有着改造积木的梦想，在儿子 James 的帮助下，他们带领了设计团队研发了一套有弹性的积木。这个名为 <a href=\"http://flexo.nz/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Flexo</a> 的系统由积木本体和连接配件（tendon）构成，配件与人体肌腱有着类似的功能，可以拉伸、弯曲甚至旋转。只要将它们扣进积木的凹槽就能组合出各种各样的结构，无论是晃动的桥梁、履带还是圆圈都可以用这种方法打造，让积木创作变得更加生动有趣。你可以通过<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/1135315686/flexo-bendable-bouncy-flexible-building-bricks\" rel=\"nofollow\">链接</a>参与众筹，入门包（100 块积木和 300 块配件）的早鸟价为 30 新西兰元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160917235137FcodP8ZEi4qpBM5t.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.499255\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160917235137ZT0kYMHWV6n5yw3D.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.746269\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160917235145EniIgGBxzqSwCv60.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"gif\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160917235140utrnfHg6kMqvyXDI.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160917235146VZiIHTGKuoU0E3rS.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160917235146AscFELqlv1fnyHt5.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div>"}